Thuletuvalu (TV5Monde)

Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Matthias von Gunten, published by TV5Monde in 2015 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/b/b6/Thuletuvalu-TV5Monde-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Thule, Greenland. The local population's survival is threatened by the melting of the icecaps. Tuvalu archipelago, Pacific Ocean. The rising water levels eat away at the coastline, unearth trees and pollute freshwater sources. Thule and Tuvalu share the same fate: climate change.
